name: Five Nights at F**kyland: Revamped
description:
After the original game had been wiped off the face of the earth, a single dev, along with a couple friends behind the scenes, had worked together to bring the game back from the dead.
One night, after the many other nights, Lala decided to have a night of debauchery, along with a lot of her fellow tubbybots, but little did she know, there was quite a few challenges in the way to make that happen.

Original Dev: Delta Storm

Holder of the old files: Devtama

Graphics/Battlers: Jordan
